{"tid":1349523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急！唔好比政府如願以償","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T09:15:48.000Z","uid":261743,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc12d42317c3ed3879ee1e320c7805949094468","tid":1349523,"uid":261743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/22/MKJ7Bk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2FMKJ7Bk.jpg&h=f034052f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋日有去發夢嘅兄弟姊妹都知<br />\n一路向西係無狗阻止過<br />\n政府就係想人搞中聯辦，之後就達成圖中第一點<br />\n<br />\n而家搵黑社會分區打人，就係想達成第二點<br />\n<br />\n當香港變成緊急狀態<br />\n大陸就可以直接接手香港<br />\n<br />\n佢地要亂，我地平亂"},{"pid":"2ee2859e7109ce2f1c1e3827209e05a6f1c73124","tid":1349523,"uid":261743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66d722025873e6dee526a6a0b9a820397c56f38f","tid":1349523,"uid":261743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cb7097d03f28dba7fea37b423625ade000f9661","tid":1349523,"uid":261743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6117a8eb5393e341625260817e2bc4509bf1c22","tid":1349523,"uid":261743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a63c3252e049af409a1e30cfb2a6667f85dc14a7","tid":1349523,"uid":261743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:36:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c8393b3a1b8b10a18c7a8fa00b94db361b8c221","tid":1349523,"uid":261743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3e6907d95ce43e53e5fc3c51c3cfcd2182aa5ef","tid":1349523,"uid":261743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8990fdd1bc301db52e98b1877fa9792d909761fc","tid":1349523,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:11:54.000Z","msg":"就係要佢出解放軍，你以為我哋只係講講吓？<br />\n香港又我冇份，香港繼續繁榮安定，我又唔會得益，只會望住樓價物價係咁升，自己人工又唔升<br />\n與其係咁，我寧願成個香港一齊死<br />\n以香港作為一粒巨大嘅政治炸彈，去撼動中國共產黨喺整個中國大陸嘅統治<br />\n30年前8964你捱得過，就睇吓你今次係咪又咁好彩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">If we burn, you burn with us!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"39f7aa6cc62b925319ce8cfce0b8fdf8cc4cb887","tid":1349523,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:15:48.000Z","msg":"一獲熟咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港比港共統治只會差落去<br />\n市民冇野輸 怕咩？"}]}